bilingual.source: I spent all my childhood in Beijing.

bilingual.source: That artist didn't have a happy childhood.
bilingual.target: 那位艺术家没有快乐的童年。

bilingual.source: It's a photo about sharing and the joy of childhood.
bilingual.target: 这是一张关于分享和童年快乐的照片。

bilingual.source: First, the Ghost of Christmas Past takes him back to his childhood and reminds Scrooge of his happier days as a child.
bilingual.target: 首先，圣诞过去之幽灵带他回到童年，提醒斯克鲁奇他童年时更快乐的日子。

bilingual.source: Think about your favorite thing from childhood which you still have.

我非常怀恋童年的时光。
我有一个美好的童年记忆。

list.abstract: 《Childhood》是一首由迈克尔·杰克逊作词并演唱的英语流行歌曲。该歌曲由索尼音乐发行于1995年，被收录在专辑《HIStory: Past, Present and Future,Book I》中。 《Childhood》曲调悠扬温婉动听，像是在倾诉着内心的感受。 迈克尔杰克逊从未有过真正属于自己的童年，只有孩子让他感到过真正的友情和欢乐，而这短暂的欢乐却成为他永恒的伤口。

yingyinNormal.en: Childhood ain't so jolly. In fact, it's rather frightening. Agree?
yingyinNormal.zh: 并不愉快的童年，事实上，周遭环境也很可怕，是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my God, Max. My childhood bank. You had a childhood bank? I didn't even have a childhood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，麦克斯，我童年的银行。你童年时期就有银行啦？我连童年都没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay Julie, so now let's start with your childhood, what was that like?
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我们从你的童年开始，你的童年是怎么样？

yingyinNormal.en: I feel strange sharing a childhood story, considering I was never a child.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟你分享我的童年故事感觉有点奇怪，鉴于我根本就没有童年。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, well, I had a wonderful childhood. Tell me about it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有个很棒的童年。和我说说。

yingyinNormal.en: How do you think I am? You've wrecked all my childhood memories.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得呢？你毁了我的童年回忆。

yingyinNormal.en: Mm-hmm. Yep. I see nothing in this box but a wasted childhood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好啊，盒子里除了空虚的童年时光空无一物。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything I went through, he went through. My childhood is missing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我经历过的每件事，它都经历过，我的童年不见了。

yingyinNormal.en: And leave him anyway, and come back here to give the children a happy childhood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后还是离开他回到这里，为了给孩子们一个美好童年。

yingyinNormal.en: Max, are you sure about this? This is the only thing you have from your childhood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 麦克斯，你确定要这样做吗？这是你童年唯一拥有的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: A Teddy bear is a source of joy and comfort and security and love. Barry was my childhood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 泰迪熊是快乐，安慰，安全和爱的源泉，巴里代表的是我的童年。

yingyinNormal.en: So, we're all here to look for your childhood Teddy bear that Auggie chewed the face off of?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以，我们都要在这儿寻找那个被奥吉咬掉脸的你童年玩的泰迪熊？

yingyinNormal.en: Aren't you at least curious what she sent? Unless it's a brand new childhood, I'm not interested.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你难道都不好奇她寄了什么来吗？除非是个全新的童年，否则我没半点兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: Caroline, my childhood is not worth $700. The most my mother ever got for me was 40 bucks and a Big Gulp.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡洛琳，我的童年不值700美元，我妈最多给过我40块和一杯超大杯汽水。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. These toys! This is like looking back at my childhood but, you know, a time before Rainbows became political.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧瞧这些玩偶，感觉就像在回顾我的童年，但当年彩虹仅仅是彩虹，不是同志象征。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll give you 600 for the bear. Sold. No, Max! That's your childhood. 700. Sold! No, Max!
yingyinNormal.zh: 那只熊我出到600美元。成交 。不行，麦克斯！那可是你的童年。700美元 。成交！不行，麦克斯！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it means you value yourself only as others value you, which is often the result of unmet childhood emotional needs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就是说只有别人看重你时，你才看重自己，一般是童年情感需要得不到满足的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: Penny, if I'm going to buy Leonard a gift, I'm going to do it right. I refuse to let him experience the same childhood trauma I did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮，如果我要给莱纳德买礼物，我一定要买得合适，我不会让他经历我童年时的创伤。

yingyinNormal.en: So Jack could be free. Now, this is the ultimate sacrifice and I understand that, but did you think about him having a normal childhood?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样杰克就自由了，这是最终极的牺牲，我很理解你，可你有没有想过让他过个正常的童年？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, Farkle. Why are we all looking so hard for the last ripped up, raggedy piece of Riley's childhood? Maybe I'm not quite ready for it to be gone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，法尔科，为什么我们都这么努力地寻找莱丽那破烂的一部分童年，也许我还没准备好让它离开。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
